# Single-player baseline: no input, no peer, no spawn_at, default
# tutorial map. Should sit perfectly still after spawn settle.
# If the pelvis trail shows non-zero velocity past tick ~30 (gravity
# settle) then something is generating phantom input.

window 1280 720
seed 1 0
out build/shots/m6_idle_baseline
aim 800 600

at  20 shot t020
at  60 shot t060
at 100 shot t100
at 150 shot t150
at 200 shot t200

at 240 end
